ğ—ªğ—µğ˜† ğ˜‚ğ˜€ğ—² ğ—¶ğ˜: Ideal for enabling seamless communication between your microservices (e.g., a frontend talking to a backend database). It inherently enhances security by keeping internal traffic private and abstracts away the dynamic nature of Pod IPs.

